description:
Great location for Carleton student! 11 minutes walking distance to Greenboro O-Train/ bus station and South Key shopping center. 5 minutes O-Train short ride to Carleton University.


This is a bright single house with 7 furnished bedrooms in South Keys. 4 rooms available for rent from Sep. 1, starting from $420 depending on the room size. These 4 rooms rent total for a group is $1755+utility. Individual student or a four-member Carleton student group is welcome.


Note: unlike other house that is empty for group rental, this house is fully furnished, no need to bring your own furniture!

Available from Sep. 1, 2020 and minimum one year lease required.


Features include:

•	All rooms with big windows and bed, newer mattress, nightstand, closet, computer table and chair;

•	All 2nd floor bedrooms are equipped with mini fridges;

•	3 full bathrooms – 1 for master bedroom, 2 shared bathrooms (one on 1st and one on 2nd floor)

•	Large eat-in kitchen with brand new stainless steel appliances. Additional freezer, microwave, table top oven, toaster, kettle;

•	All shining hardwood/ceramic floors, no carpet;

•	Lots of common areas;

•	2-car driveway included;

•	Recreation room and lots of storage space in basement;

•	Washing machine, dryer, dishwasher, central A/C;

•	No pets. No indoor smoking. No noise to neighbors.

•	Contact George by text(preferred) or phone 613-8082721 or by email
